      "content": "but there's nothing to discover. there's just nothing. it's not some growth process, it's just... emptiness. i feel like i'm just a ghost haunting this house. i see photos of us and it feels like they're from a different lifetime. it's like i'm already dead, just walking around without knowing it. how am i supposed to \"find peace\" when the only person who made life worth living is gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
